OL,3,CCornwall mum says 'mouldy' and 'damp'
OL,4,Csocial housing gave her children asthma
OL,6,FA mother from Cornwall says she feels
OL,7,Fangry that the severe damp and mould
OL,8,Fin her social housing has been harming
OL,9,Fher children.
OL,11,FJasmine Betts, from Penryn, says a
OL,12,Fdoctor has confirmed her daughters,
OL,13,Faged 4 and 5, both have recently
OL,14,Fdiagnosed asthma which has been been
OL,15,Fbrought on by the conditions in their
OL,16,Fhome.
OL,18,F"It's really worrying, because as a
OL,19,Fmum, I have to protect my children and
OL,20,FI feel like I can't."
