OL,3,CCornwall mum says 'mouldy' and 'damp'
OL,4,Csocial housing gave her children asthma
OL,6,F"I'm also pregnant as well, which I
OL,7,Freally thought that the works would
OL,8,Fhave been done way before now. I
OL,9,Fdidn't think I'd be in a situation
OL,10,Fwhere potentially I could be bringing
OL,11,Fa newborn baby into this house."
OL,13,FThe parent says she has been
OL,14,Fcomplaining about the damp problems at
OL,15,Fher home since she and her three
OL,16,Fchildren moved into the property in
OL,17,F2020. Over the years she estimates
OL,18,Fthousands of pounds worth of damages
OL,19,Fto their flooring, clothing and
OL,20,Felectrical devices.
