OL,3,CCornwall mum says 'mouldy' and 'damp'
OL,4,Csocial housing gave her children asthma
OL,6,FJasmine says the worst room is her
OL,7,Fbedroom which has black mould across
OL,8,Fthe ceiling and under the window it
OL,9,F"streams with water".
OL,11,FShe says the problem has become so
OL,12,Fsevere she and her partner, who also
OL,13,Fhas asthma, now sleep on a sofa in the
OL,14,Fliving room.
OL,16,F"It was affecting his chest so for
OL,17,Fthree or four months he was getting
OL,18,Fdifferent antibiotics and steroids and
OL,19,Fin the end we thought we just can't
OL,20,Fsleep in here anymore."
