OL,6,FA surveyors report in January seen by
OL,7,FITV News West Country has confirmed
OL,8,Fthe property has leaks in the roof and
OL,9,Flittle to no insulation in the loft
OL,10,Fand in the walls.
OL,12,FDue to the severity of the repairs
OL,13,Fneeded Jasmine has been told the
OL,14,Ffamily will need to move out of the
OL,15,Fproperty.
