OL,3,CCornwall mum says 'mouldy' and 'damp'
OL,4,Csocial housing gave her children asthma
OL,6,FLast month Cornwall Housing offered
OL,7,FJasmine and her family a new property
OL,8,Fin Penryn. Jasmine says whilst she
OL,9,Fwants to move to this new
OL,10,Faccommodation she wants to be properly
OL,11,Fcompensated for the health and
OL,12,Ffinancial costs this has put on her
OL,13,Ffamily.J"The money that they've
OL,14,Foffered us does not even cover the
OL,15,Ftoys that we've had to buy, let alone
OL,16,Fthe furniture and our devices that are
OL,17,Fdamaged and I just feel absolutely
OL,18,Fdisgusted in how we've been treated
OL,19,Fand what they have put my children
OL,20,Fthrough."
