OL,4,Csocial housing gave her children asthma
OL,6,FCornwall Housing told ITV News West
OL,7,FCountry there are currently more than
OL,8,F750 households living in temporary
OL,9,Faccommodation in Cornwall and the
OL,10,Fpressures of finding the right home
OL,11,Ffor someone can be more acute if a
OL,12,Fhousehold has "specific location
OL,13,Frequirements".
OL,15,FIn a statement they said: "While we
OL,16,Fare unable to go into specific details
OL,17,Fin this case, we have been working
OL,18,Fwith the family for many months over
OL,19,Fthe issues raised and have offered
OL,20,Falternative accommodation."
