OL,6,F"In some cases where alternative
OL,7,Faccommodation has been refused, we may
OL,8,Foffer another property.
OL,10,F"This accommodation will be placed on
OL,11,Fhold and will not be available to
OL,12,Fbidders on Homechoice while we await a
OL,13,Fdecision from the tenants."
OL,15,F"There are currently more than 750
OL,16,Fhouseholds living temporary
OL,17,Faccommodation in Cornwall and these
OL,18,Fpressures can be more acute if a
OL,19,Fhousehold has specific location
OL,20,Frequirements."
